snippet.title: Card Shark - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Card Shark is available now on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/card-shark-switch/

Card Shark is an adventure game full of cunning, intrigue, and delectable deceit. Enter a world where you’ll need to play your opponents better than you play your cards.

#CardShark #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch
